1
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:29,980
=The Youth Memories=

2
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,980
=Episode 37=

3
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,440
Mr. Ye.

4
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:06,040
I know what happened.

5
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,030
So, you came here

6
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,200
to laugh at me, right?

7
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,160
Mr. Xiao, now that

8
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,720
you know what happened,

9
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,600
I won't bother to entertain you.

10
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:23,480
Guohua,

11
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,640
I came to help you.

12
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:29,960
Help me?

13
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,040
Fine.

14
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:39,960
You win.

15
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:41,720
I admit

16
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,840
that you're the most successful

17
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,240
and the best man.

18
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,520
I'm always inferior to you, OK?

19
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,240
Stop gibbering.

20
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,440
Look.

21
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,520
What's the difference?

22
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,560
You can't tell, huh?

23
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,000
Be professional, OK?

24
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,600
I do foreign trade, not technology.

25
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,640
This is

26
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,320
our drawing.

27
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,960
And this one is Li Shangyou's.

28
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,440
Only the core components are different.

29
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,560
So, they have different qualities.

30
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,040
My engineers

31
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,960
have been working on the problem

32
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,040
that core components are
sometimes unstable

33
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,320
and haven't solved it until recently.

34
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,800
That's why

35
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,520
I dared to take your order.

36
00:03:59,200 --> 00:03:59,760
And of course,

37
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:02,640
this research has been confidential.

38
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,840
So Heizi didn't know

39
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,160
what he gave Li Shangyou

40
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,320
wasn't the latest one.

41
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,120
I can take this order

42
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,880
and have all core components replaced

43
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,760
to meet international requirements.

44
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,280
Will this work?

45
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:39,160
Have I ever failed you once?

46
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,680
No, never.

47
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,400
Chunsheng,

48
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,840
why do you still help me?

49
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,760
Because you're my buddy.

50
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,160
My best buddy.

51
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,160
Do you trust me?

52
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,400
It's not time to celebrate yet.

53
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,960
I have one condition.

54
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,520
Tell me.

55
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:32,920
Chunsheng,

56
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:36,240
will you really take Ye Guohua's order?

57
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,600
That's quite a big one.

58
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,680
Products for Nanjing
will be delivered by the end of March.

59
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:45,960
Products for Southeast Asia, April.

60
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:47,880
Let's do this, Tian.

61
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,880
Postpone these two batches

62
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,280
until the Spring Festival is over.

63
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,040
Spare one production line

64
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,440
for the machines for Huasheng.

65
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,000
Fine.

66
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,520
Now that you promised him,

67
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,800
I won't argue.

68
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:04,920
You're helpful

69
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,240
and I won't drag you down.

70
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,120
But you have to

71
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:12,080
promise me one thing.

72
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:13,840
Speak.

73
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:17,040
He must pay the market price.

74
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,200
We can't lose money.

75
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
My workers

76
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,760
can't work for nothing.

77
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,320
OK.

78
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,720
They won't work for nothing.

79
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,600
What's more,

80
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,560
let's give them a big bonus
by the end of the year.

81
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,600
What do you think?

82
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,920
OK. It's a deal, then.

83
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:37,780
(Chunxiao Health Care)

84
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,400
Be careful.

85
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:38,880
Careful.

86
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,160
Tian,

87
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,320
what's wrong with everybody?

88
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,720
They look unwell.

89
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,080
Are they sick?

90
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,320
No idea.

91
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,640
Today, Cai even asked for leave,
saying he had a cold.

92
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,240
He's a strong man

93
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,520
and exercises every day.

94
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,320
But a cold got him down.

95
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,160
- Everyone's working hard lately.
- Come on, give me a hand.

96
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,720
It's normal that they get weaker.

97
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,640
It's OK.

98
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,520
I'll have someone
buy some medicine for flu

99
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,720
and make do with these days.

100
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,840
You can't do that.

101
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,760
What if they feel unwell

102
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,240
and get hurt when moving things?

103
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,640
How about this?

104
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,920
Have them go to the hospital for a check.

105
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,240
They can't.

106
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,600
Time is pressing for too much work.

107
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,880
With fewer men,
we can't complete the mission.

108
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,560
Chunsheng.

109
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:24,880
Chunsheng.

110
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:28,240
How about you mobilize them

111
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,200
to work during the Spring Festival?

112
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,600
No way.

113
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,080
Any festival will do,
except the Spring Festival.

114
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,320
Think about it.

115
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,640
Workers work for the whole year

116
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,600
just to get back to their families

117
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,560
and enjoy a happy festival together.

118
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,760
You're right.

119
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,840
But our production...

120
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,400
Tian,

121
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,120
it's no hurry for a couple of days.

122
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,400
Well,

123
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,400
the customs declaration
will take some days.

124
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,360
Give our workers a big bonus

125
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,360
and let them enjoy a good festival.

126
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,560
It's really generous of you.

127
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,400
Don't make fun of me.

128
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,640
I'm a small businessman,

129
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:01,840
not a capitalist.

130
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:06,420
(Police)

131
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,440
Xiaohui?

132
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,280
Long time no see.

133
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,760
Li Shangyou didn't hurt you, did he?

134
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,240
Over all these years,

135
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,520
you haven't got
even a little bit smarter.

136
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,760
Don't be silly.

137
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,200
What kind of man is Li Shangyou?

138
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,880
How could you trust him?

139
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,840
How did you know this?

140
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,560
Yanqiu told me.

141
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,320
Actually, in the past few years,

142
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,360
we've been in touch.

143
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,960
Li Shangyou threatened me
with your life.

144
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:13,000
I hurt you really a lot

145
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,840
and I can't let anyone else hurt you.

146
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,560
Come on.

147
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,440
Now, you've realized it?

148
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,280
But what did you do?

149
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,800
I've lived most of my life

150
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:35,000
(Silence)
and now I know I've done a lot wrong.

151
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,600
It's been years

152
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,960
and I've wanted to apologize.

153
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,440
I want to say sorry.

154
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,320
But I didn't find you.

155
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,040
And I didn't expect

156
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,800
that I could see you again.

157
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,120
Heizi,

158
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:02,280
behave yourself in jail.

159
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,520
Try to come out early.

160
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:08,080
And then,
come to Hong Kong, China for me.

161
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:09,720
I'll be waiting.

162
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,320
Tian,

163
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,760
drive me to the airport, please.

164
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:33,920
Leaving already?

165
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,480
Chunsheng.

166
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,360
Get up. Take off your clothes

167
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:01,760
and have a bath before you sleep.

168
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:02,480
Come on.

169
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,440
Xiaomei,

170
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,240
I'm OK.

171
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,440
Let me lie for a moment.

172
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,120
Chunsheng,

173
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,280
you need some rest.

174
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,440
For production,

175
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,680
Tian and his men are watching.

176
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,360
You don't need to worry that much.

177
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,320
Guohua's products

178
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:24,000
were finally returned from the Customs.

179
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,760
New products are in urgent need.

180
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,000
I have to ask my workers

181
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,480
to work overtime.

182
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,880
Everything's finally back
on the right path

183
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,880
and nothing can go wrong again.

184
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:44,600
Xiaomei,

185
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,240
wait until the Spring Festival.

186
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:52,080
Then I'll spend more time
with you and Beibei.

187
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,440
It's OK

188
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,480
that you have no time for us.

189
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,080
I just worry about your health.

190
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:33,440
Chunsheng,

191
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:36,040
listen to me and go back for some rest.

192
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,040
Tian, the products for Guohua

193
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,760
are going through the customs declaration.

194
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,280
It'll be approved soon.

195
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:41,920
Check this.

196
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,480
I know.

197
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,960
Our new production line

198
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,240
has been functioning day and night.

199
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:48,320
Don't... Don't worry.
I'll stay and watch.

200
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:49,960
You haven't slept
for two days and nights.

201
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:50,920
Go get some sleep.

202
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,200
It's OK. I'm fine.

203
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,280
There you are, Xiaomei.

204
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,960
Xiaomei, what did you come for?

205
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,720
If I still didn't come,

206
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,920
someone would even be
too busy to have lunch.

207
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,400
You think no one can restrain you, huh?

208
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:06,680
Extra food for you.

209
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,200
Dumplings I made.

210
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,600
Taste some.

211
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,200
Oh, extra food?

212
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,600
Xiaomei is busy at work

213
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,520
and it's rare for us

214
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:15,280
to taste her dumplings.

215
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,280
Dr. Tong has limited energy.

216
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,880
She spared some time for the dumplings

217
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,840
and do cherish them.

218
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,760
Don't worry, Dr. Tong.

219
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,000
Based on the current producing pace,

220
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:29,080
products for Guohua will be done soon.

221
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,840
Warm tip from Dr. Tong.

222
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:34,680
When it's lunchtime, have lunch

223
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,760
instead of talking about work.

224
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,160
Eat the dumplings. Or they'll get cold.

225
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,400
Some vinegar is in it.

226
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,040
It is?

227
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,640
Tian,

228
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:45,120
do you remember back in the stack room,

229
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:47,680
Xiaomei's shout scared me so much

230
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,200
that I didn't finish my dumplings.

231
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,760
I heard about that.

232
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,440
The secret girl in the stack room.

233
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,000
Exactly.

234
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:58,000
Come on. Don't make fun of me.

235
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,880
Go. Go have lunch.

236
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,440
Let's go for the dumplings.

237
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,160
OK, go.

