510
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:48,200
you wouldn't pick me.

511
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:51,520
Guohua, that's not true.

512
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:55,840
I feel inferior, too.

513
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,480
