518
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,080
That year,

519
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:18,160
I was obsessed
with the ideal love from Chunsheng

520
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,560
and meanwhile,

521
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:22,160
I wanted a stable life from you.

522
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,320
Actually,

523
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:28,920
