535
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,640
my dream,

536
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,240
and also

537
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:06,760
another kind of stable life.

538
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:15,120
Xiao Chunsheng and I were done.

539
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:19,040
Since the moment
he chose Tong Xiaomei,

540
00:26:20,320 --> 00:26:22,120
he had nothing to do with me.

541
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,240
After all, a woman like me

542
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,760
