543
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,800
See? I'm just this kind of woman,

544
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:35,920
very selfish.

545
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:39,920
Hongling,

546
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:42,880
I don't care if you're selfish

547
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,240
