00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,960
The Customs declaration
hasn't been approved yet.

699
00:35:04,720 --> 00:35:05,520
But it usually takes

700
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:07,240
a day or two, doesn't it?

701
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,640
It's been over a month.

702
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,680
Is Chen Hongjun

703
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:18,200
doing some dirty tricks?

704
00:35:19,080 --> 00:35:20,200
I went to see him.

