00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:24,480
It's urgent. Don't keep me guessing.

728
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:31,360
Chunsheng, it's a critical moment.

729
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:34,360
You can't still be thinking
he's our best buddy, huh?

730
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,000
He's no longer

731
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,520
the Chen Hongjun we used to know.

